移除推荐信息流推广=type=http-response, pattern=^https:\/\/api\.zhihu\.com\/feed\/render\/tab\/config\?, script-path=https://kelee.one/Resource/JavaScript/Zhihu/Zhihu_remove_ads.js, requires-body=true

